Re-syncing to a newer upstream release
--------------------------------------
1. Re-fetch skills/ponytail/SKILL.md from the upstream repo at the desired tag.
2. Overwrite SKILL.md in this directory (keep it byte-for-byte for a clean diff).
3. Update the Version / Commit / Vendored fields above.
4. Add a CHANGELOG.md entry under [Unreleased] noting the bump.


